snippet.textDisplay: This concept could work today for some issues using Machine Learning image recognition to identify likely causes of some faults. A driver would send an image or a description of what they can see / sense is wrong with the car and a database could see if there are any similar cases. Or alternatively you could just have a simple subscription model: video call a mechanic on demand. Would need some thinking through but it’s definitely not impossible.
